These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
Color: mauve, emerald, light-blue
1. Color:mauve is on the far right##1
2. Color:mauve is not to the left of Color:emerald##8
3. Color:light-blue is somewhere to the left of Color:emerald##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Color   | light-blue | emerald | mauve |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
Color: light-blue, aquamarine, orange
1. Color:orange is not to the left of Color:light-blue##8
2. Color:orange is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Color   | light-blue | orange | aquamarine |

 #################################
 
